      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOSTON BANNER (1) is suited by the inside draw. Latest effort finished 2nd on May 1 over 401m at this track behind Zipping Hopkins beaten 3 lengths (23.16) in a Mix 2/3. Rates a leading player and sure to be in this for a long way. HISTORY'S COMING (4) goes very well at the course with two wins and a placing from four starts. Hit the frame latest (22.64) when second at Maitland in a Mix 2/3. Looks suited here and can measure up. STILL AVAILABLE (6) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage third, beaten 4.5 lengths (23.23) at this track in a Mix 2/3 over 401m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Winning chance. FANTASIA QUEEN (2) will need to repeat last run to feature.",
